data.description: This property serves as an ideal starter family home, offering a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. With three bedrooms and two baths, it provides ample space for a growing family. The 1,800 sq ft layout ensures a cozy yet manageable environment, and the recent updates guarantee modern amenities. The expansive five-acre lot not only provides a sense of privacy but also allows for outdoor activities and future expansion. The peaceful rural location fosters a family-friendly atmosphere, creatlng a welcoming and secure environment for those starting their homeownership journey. If you have any questions or concerns text or call 580-695-5063 or email charles.dollar@kw.com
